.DT
add_property
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
add_property

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_property -  Adds a property onto the object.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
varargs int add_property(string var,
mixed val,
int tim)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^var%^RESET%^ - the name of the property
%^BOLD%^val%^RESET%^ - the value to give the property
%^BOLD%^tim%^RESET%^ - the time before the property should time out
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 if it succeeded, 0 if it failed.

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/basic/property.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

Adds a property onto the object.  Allows you to add a property
onto the current object.  You can also set a time for the property
to last.
.EP

